    "body":  "Description:\nTo help demo viewers understand what the dashboard is showing, simulate a scoped \"Manager View\" without adding any backend role logic.\n\nRequested UI Changes:\n\nAdd a static label near the top:\n🧑‍💼 Viewing: My Team\n\nAdd a non-functional dropdown labeled Scope: with values:\n\nMy Team\n\nMy Org\n\nAll Users\n(Set default to “My Team”)\n\nUpdate Quick Actions to reflect the context, e.g.,\n\n“View My Team’s Qualifications”\n\n“Review Team Assessments”\n\nNo backend or dynamic filtering needed at this stage. Static UI only.",
